description:
Enjoy this short gameplay sizzle of DOOM: The Dark Ages. 

Developed by id Software, DOOM: The Dark Ages is the prequel to the critically acclaimed DOOM (2016) and DOOM Eternal that tells an epic cinematic story of the DOOM Slayer’s rage. In this third installment of the modern DOOM series, players will step into the blood-stained boots of the DOOM Slayer, in this never-before-seen dark and sinister medieval war against Hell.    

Coming May 15, 2025. Pre-order on PlayStation®5.

author: PlayStation
description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10008503/

"Step into the stunning, surreal world of Clair Obscur: Expedition 33, launching April 24, 2025, on PlayStation 5. Each year, the Paintress marks her cursed number, erasing the lives of those in Lumière who are that age. Tomorrow, she will paint “33.”

Explore vibrant environments like Ancient Sanctuary and Gestral Village, uncover secrets, and tackle side quests across the expansive overworld. Set up camp to strengthen weapons, bond with teammates, and take a break between defeating Nevrons to spin the record player (playing the game’s OST!).

Meet Monoco (voiced by Rich Keeble), a shape-shifting Gestral with a penchant for collecting the feet of his enemies, and Esquie (voiced by Maxence Cazorla), a larger-than-life companion who lets you ride on his back to traverse and explore the stunning Belle Époque-inspired world. 

Clair Obscur: Expedition 33 launches April 24, 2025. Pre-order now on the PlayStation Store or at your local reta

author: PlayStation
description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10013154

Return to the world of Sword of the Necromancer like never before! Resurrection is a 3D remake of the original game, completely reimagined with new graphics and gameplay mechanics.
Dive into an adventure full of emotions, strategy, and action, with an artistic style inspired by the classics of the 6th generation console era, now brought to the modern age.

Turn your foes into allies. Use the forbidden powers of the Sword of the Necromancer and help Tama reach the dungeon's depths in order to gain enough power to bring Koko back from the dead.

FEATURES
- 3D Graphics inspired by a legendary era
- Fluid and dynamic combat system
- Customize your summons with the "Tactics" system
- Remastered soundtrack and new themes
- Infinite replayability
- Local Co-op Mode

Sword of the Necromancer Resurrection is available now!

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4gameplay
title: Sword of the Necromancer: Resurrection - Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 games
